| complex 6 | 385/490                         | τ<sub>1</sub> = 1.0; τ<sub>2</sub> = 8.4 | 2.4   |
| complex 7 | 379/542                         | τ = 1029.7 | 20.6  |
| complex 8 | 380/421                         | τ<sub>1</sub> = 1.0; τ<sub>2</sub> = 6.5 | 2.3   |
| complex 9 | 320/542,614                     | τ<sub>Tb</sub> = 785.1/τ<sub>Eu</sub> = 436.3 | 15.3 |
| complex 10| 322/542,614                     | τ<sub>Tb</sub> = 705.4/τ<sub>Eu</sub> = 405.1 | 13.9 |
| Nd(TFI)<sub>3</sub>(bpy)<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref47"></xref> | 343/1060 | τ = 9.9 | 4.0 |
| Nd(TFI)<sub>3</sub>(phen)<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref47"></xref> | 358/1060 | τ = 11.3 | 4.6 |

| [Eu<sub>2</sub>L<sub>3</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>OH)<sub>2</sub>(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>4</sub> <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref13"></xref> | 320/614 | τ = 269.8 | 15.0 |
